metadata.name: Favourites GET /api/v1/favourites with limit param sets the correct pagination header for the next path

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT "favourites"."id" AS t0_r0, "favourites"."created_at" AS t0_r1, "favourites"."updated_at" AS t0_r2, "favourites"."account_id" AS t0_r3, "favourites"."status_id" AS t0_r4, "statuses"."id" AS t1_r0, "statuses"."uri" AS t1_r1, "statuses"."text" AS t1_r2, "statuses"."created_at" AS t1_r3, "statuses"."updated_at" AS t1_r4, "statuses"."in_reply_to_id" AS t1_r5, "statuses"."reblog_of_id" AS t1_r6, "statuses"."url" AS t1_r7, "statuses"."sensitive" AS t1_r8, "statuses"."visibility" AS t1_r9, "statuses"."spoiler_text" AS t1_r10, "statuses"."reply" AS t1_r11, "statuses"."language" AS t1_r12, "statuses"."conversation_id" AS t1_r13, "statuses"."local" AS t1_r14, "statuses"."account_id" AS t1_r15, "statuses"."application_id" AS t1_r16, "statuses"."in_reply_to_account_id" AS t1_r17, "statuses"."poll_id" AS t1_r18, "statuses"."deleted_at" AS t1_r19, "statuses"."edited_at" AS t1_r20, "statuses"."trendable" AS t1_r21, "statuses"."ordered_media_attachment_ids" AS t1_r22 FROM "favourites" INNER JOIN "statuses" ON "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = "favourites"."status_id" WHERE "favourites"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY "favourites"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" IN ($1, $2) ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC

sql_query.sql: SELECT "custom_filter_keywords"."id" AS t0_r0, "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" AS t0_r1, "custom_filter_keywords"."keyword" AS t0_r2, "custom_filter_keywords"."whole_word" AS t0_r3, "custom_filter_keywords"."created_at" AS t0_r4, "custom_filter_keywords"."updated_at" AS t0_r5, "custom_filter"."id" AS t1_r0, "custom_filter"."account_id" AS t1_r1, "custom_filter"."expires_at" AS t1_r2, "custom_filter"."phrase" AS t1_r3, "custom_filter"."context" AS t1_r4, "custom_filter"."created_at" AS t1_r5, "custom_filter"."updated_at" AS t1_r6, "custom_filter"."action" AS t1_r7 FROM "custom_filter_keywords" LEFT OUTER JOIN "custom_filters" "custom_filter" ON "custom_filter"."id" = "custom_filter_keywords"."custom_filter_id" WHERE "custom_filter"."account_id" = $1 AND (expires_at IS NULL OR expires_at > NOW())
